I've had this game for a long time, and I really enjoy it. The puzzles and graphics are great! I hope this game gets updated for the iPhone 6. Can't believe people are complaining that the developer is charging a dollar (yes a whole dollar) for the extra downloadable levels that he/she took all the time to create and program. Clearly this person should just keep making new levels for us for free because at some point we paid a dollar for this game when we originally bought it. There are no iaps that effect the game play, like timers, that hurt the game. Don't understand why people complain about something that's completely optional. If you play through the original game that you bought and like it- download the extra levels for a buck. If you don't want to pay for extra levels, than don't. This is great game that I've really enjoyed. No complaints from me. Hope to see more games from this developer in the future! If you like quality puzzle games, I highly recommend checking this game out.
